title: Becks & Posh: Kedgeree
summary: The recipe Becks & Posh: Kedgeree could satisfy your Scottish craving in roughly 45 minutes. This recipe makes 6 servings with 1005 calories, 54g of protein, and 33g of fat each. For $5.77 per serving, this recipe covers 41% of your daily requirements of vitamins and minerals. This recipe from becksposhnosh.blogspot.com has 1 fans. It is a good option if you're following a gluten free and pescatarian diet. It works well as a main course. Head to the store and pick up lemons, basmati rice, milk, and a few other things to make it today. To use up the milk you could follow this main course with the Milky Way Brownie Bites as a dessert. All things considered, we decided this recipe deserves a spoonacular score of 75%. This score is solid. Similar recipes are Posh Piggies, Posh spice cake, and Posh ice cream sandwiches.
